#originalTopic=should-abortion-be-legal
The only women who suffer psychologically are the ones who buy into the evangelicals' irrational anti-abortion propaganda. Women who do not are fine.However, the issue is not whether women suffer. The issue is whether women should have a right to abort a fetus or not. The answer is that they should and do have that right, because in all reason, a fetus does not have rights.